                <span class="p-tag">IoT API</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="portfolio-info">
            <div class="portfolio-meta">
              <span class="portfolio-category">Création Web Full-Stack</span>
              <span class="portfolio-year font-mono">2026</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="portfolio-title">DHM-Tech — Pilotage Industriel</h2>
            <p class="portfolio-desc">Dashboard SaaS temps réel d'observabilité IoT. Intègre l'isolation de données Supabase (RLS), un temps de chargement sous la seconde et une conformité NIS2 native.</p>
            <div class="portfolio-metrics" aria-label="Métriques du projet">
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-icon metric-green" aria-hidden="true">⚡</span>
                <span class="metric-value">0.7s</span>
                <span class="metric-label">LCP Speed</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-icon metric-blue" aria-hidden="true">🛡</span>
                <span class="metric-value">12k+</span>
                <span class="metric-label">Visites/j</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-icon metric-purple" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
                <span class="metric-value">100/100</span>
                <span class="metric-label">SEO</span>
