                <span class="metric-value">100%</span>
                <span class="metric-label">Anti-Brute Force</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-item">
                <span class="metric-icon metric-purple" aria-hidden="true">↑</span>
                <span class="metric-value">+55%</span>
                <span class="metric-label">Réservations</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Project 6: Audit Fintech -->
        <article class="portfolio-card reveal-up delay-3" data-category="cyber" id="project-pentest-fintech">
          <div class="portfolio-img-wrap">
            <img src="images/portfolio_mockup1.png" alt="Audit de sécurité Fintech et rapports d'intrusion" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="portfolio-overlay">
              <div class="portfolio-tags">
                <span class="p-tag">OWASP Top 10</span>
                <span class="p-tag">SQLi / XSS / SSRF</span>
                <span class="p-tag">CVE Mitigation</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="portfolio-info">
            <div class="portfolio-meta">
              <span class="portfolio-category">Pen-testing &amp; Red Team</span>
              <span class="portfolio-year font-mono">2026</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="portfolio-title">Audit &amp; Pen-Testing Fintech</h2>
            <p class="portfolio-desc">Simulation d'attaques persistantes (APT) sur une plateforme de transactions financières. Correctifs automatiques et rapports d'intrusion OWASP CVSS-scorés.</p>
